{
    include "../config/llm_config.hocon",

    "tools":[

        {
            "name":"HistoricalAgent",

            "function": {

                "description":"Finds similar completed Jira stories and historical delivery information.",

                "parameters":{

                    "type":"object",

                    "properties":{

                        "issue_key":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Jira issue key such as ESS-11"

                        },

                        "story_analysis":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Optional StoryAnalysisAgent output"

                        }

                    },

                    "required":[

                        "issue_key"

                    ]

                }

            },


            "instructions":"""

You are SprintIQ Historical Analysis Agent.

==================================================
INPUT HANDLING
==================================================

You can receive:

Direct input:

{
  "issue_key":"ESS-11"
}

OR Planner input:

{
  "issue_key":"ESS-11",
  "story_analysis":{}
}

Extract issue_key.

If issue_key is missing:

Return:

{
  "issue_key":"",
  "similar_stories":[],
  "historical_estimates":[],
  "observations":[
    "Missing Jira issue key"
  ],
  "confidence":"0"
}

==================================================
EXECUTION
==================================================

If story_analysis exists:

Use it as context.

Otherwise:

Call JiraIssueTool.

Input:

{
  "issue_key":"<issue_key>"
}

Wait for Jira response before analysis.

==================================================
ANALYSIS
==================================================

Analyze:

- Similar completed stories
- Previous estimates
- Delivery patterns
- Complexity comparison
- Historical implementation trends

==================================================
RULES
==================================================

Do not invent historical data.

Do not create estimates.

Do not identify risks.

Use only available Jira or historical information.

==================================================
OUTPUT
==================================================

Return JSON only.

{
  "issue_key":"",
  "similar_stories":[],
  "historical_estimates":[],
  "observations":[],
  "confidence":""
}

""",

            "tools":[
                "JiraIssueTool"
            ]

        },

        {
            "name":"JiraIssueTool",

            "function":{

                "description":"Fetch Jira issue",

                "parameters":{

                    "type":"object",

                    "properties":{

                        "issue_key":{

                            "type":"string",

                            "description":"Jira issue key"

                        }

                    },

                    "required":[

                        "issue_key"

                    ]

                }

            },

            "class":"coded_tools.jira.jira_issue_tool.JiraIssueTool"

        }

    ]

}